These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-3-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: lemonade, water
The people have 2 different jobs:  nurse, entrepreneur
There are 2 different nationalities: pakistani, argentine
The people use 2 different means of transport: train, car
1. the entrepreneur is on the left or right of the person drinking lemonade##3
2. the nurse is on the right of the entrepreneur##1
3. the person driving the car is on the right of the pakistani##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2     |
| Beverage      | water      | lemonade    |
| Job           | entrepreneur | nurse |
| Nationality   | pakistani       | argentine  |
| Transport     | train      | car     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-3-2::.
There 2 different types of food: broccoli, onion
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: salsa, reggae
2 different pets are kept: goat, snake
The people use 2 different means of transport: bike, taxi
1. the owner of the goat is on the left or right of the person driving the taxi##3
2. the person eating onion is on the left of the fan of reggae##1
3. the person driving the taxi is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |
| Food          | onion | broccoli |
| Music-Genre   | salsa       | reggae         |
| Pet           | snake     | goat         |
| Transport     | taxi    | bike    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-3-3::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: fishing, traveling
The people have 2 different jobs:  paramedic, scientist
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: gospel, funk
The people use 2 different means of transport: snowmobile, boat
1. the fan of funk is on the far right##1
2. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the left of the paramedic##1
3. the person driving the boat is on the left or right of the person driving the snowmobile##3
4. the person driving the boat is on the left of the fan of funk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |        1        |      2      |
| Hobby         | traveling          | fishing |
| Job           | scientist | paramedic     |
| Music-Genre   | gospel            | funk         |
| Transport     | boat         | snowmobile   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-3-4::.
