2. the person drinking 7up is the owner of the bird##1
3. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the person watching documentary movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |
| Beverage      | 7up     | iced-tea   |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary    | fantasy |
| Music-Genre   | rock   | metal |
| Pet           | bird | horse    |

