.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-3-20::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: mirinda, almond-milk
There 2 different types of food: garlic, nectarine
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: pop, rock
The people use 2 different means of transport: snowmobile, roller
1. the fan of rock is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
2. the person eating garlic is the fan of pop##1
3. the fan of pop is the person driving the roller##1
4. the person driving the snowmobile is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |
| Beverage      | almond-milk     | mirinda |
| Food          | nectarine   | garlic |
| Music-Genre   | rock     | pop     |
| Transport     | snowmobile | roller     |

 